r\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Custom Drone Storage Case<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7cc971e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7cc971e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1e308a8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1e308a8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a4b07df e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a4b07df\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-341e862 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"341e862\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Drone_case_open-1024x683.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1721\" alt=\"drone case open\" srcset=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Drone_case_open-1024x683.png 1024w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Drone_case_open-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Drone_case_open-768x512.png 768w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Drone_case_open.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"  title=\"Custom Drone Storage Case\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-93c8138 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"93c8138\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ab58315 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"ab58315\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dbe9345 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"dbe9345\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Drone_case_closed-1024x683.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1720\" alt=\"drone case closed\" srcset=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Drone_case_closed-1024x683.png 1024w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Drone_case_closed-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Drone_case_closed-768x512.png 768w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Drone_case_closed.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"  title=\"Custom Drone Storage Case\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6c3d03b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"6c3d03b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-19dde8d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"19dde8d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>This project involved designing and manufacturing a custom carrying case for a BetaFPV Meteor 75 Pro drone and its accessories using Fusion 360 and my personal Bambu Lab A1 Mini 3D printer.<\/p><p>Rather than using a generic storage solution, I designed the case specifically around the dimensions of the drone and its equipment, creating dedicated compartments for the drone, batteries, charging hub and charging cable. The aim was to provide a compact, protective and well-organised storage solution for transport and everyday use.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-661c71c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"661c71c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><a href=\"http:\/\/Overview\">Project Information\n<\/a><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fe1a476 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fe1a476\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Software<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>Fusion 360<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><strong>Manufacturing<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>FDM 3D Printing<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><strong>Printer<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>Bambu Lab A1 Mini<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><strong>Material<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>PLA<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><strong>Project Type<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>Personal Project<\/p><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d03181a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d03181a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><a href=\"http:\/\/Overview\">Design Highlights<\/a><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8e103e5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8e103e5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The case incorporates several functional features to improve usability and durability:<\/p><ul><li>Integrated living hinge connecting the lid and base<\/li><li>Mechanical latch secured using two M3 screws<\/li><li>Dedicated compartments for the drone and accessories<\/li><li>Battery holders to prevent movement during transport<\/li><li>Integrated cable management<\/li><li>Foam insert to protect the drone from impacts<\/li><\/ul><p>The internal layout was designed to maximise the use of available space while ensuring each component remained secure during transport.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c6d0b40 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c6d0b40\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><a href=\"http:\/\/Overview\">Engineering Considerations<\/a><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eb780e0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"eb780e0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The project required balancing structural strength, ease of use and printability.<\/p><p>Particular attention was given to the hinge and closing mechanism to ensure the case could be repeatedly opened and closed without compromising rigidity. The internal compartments were designed around the dimensions of each accessory to minimise movement, while additional foam and hook-and-loop straps were incorporated where greater protection or flexibility was required.<\/p><p>This project provided practical experience in enclosure design, mechanical assemblies and designing around existing hardware.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c5c60b0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c5c60b0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><a href=\"http:\/\/Overview\">Engineering Skills Applied<\/a><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-de093cd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"de093cd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li>Parametric CAD modelling in Fusion 360<\/li><li>Enclosure and packaging design<\/li><li>Assembly design<\/li><li>Hinge and latch design<\/li><li>Design for Additive Manufacturing (DfAM)<\/li><li>Functional product design<\/li><li>Rapid prototyping<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-91e36f0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"91e36f0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><a href=\"http:\/\/Overview\">Future Improvements<\/a><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-97345b9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"97345b9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A future version could incorporate a more compact locking mechanism and explore alternative designs to further improve durability and reduce the number of additional hardware components required.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u2190 Back to 3D Printing Projects Custom Drone Storage Case This project involved designing and manufacturing a custom carrying case for a BetaFPV Meteor 75 Pro drone and its accessories using Fusion 360 and my personal Bambu Lab A1 Mini 3D printer. Rather than using a generic storage solution, I designed the case specifically around [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"no-sidebar","site-content-layout":"page-builder","ast-site-content-layout":"full-width-container","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"","site-post-title":"","ast-breadcrumbs-content":"","ast-featured-img":"disabled","footer-sml-layout":"","ast-disable-related-posts":"","theme-transparent-header-meta":"","adv-header-id-meta":"","stick-header-meta":"","header-above-stick-meta":"","header-main-stick-meta":"","header-below-stick-meta":"","astra-migrate-meta-layouts":"default","ast-page-background-enabled":"default","ast-page-background-meta":{"desktop":{"background-color":"var(--ast-global-color-4)","background-image":"","background-repeat":"repeat","b